This project orchestrates several external programs (invoked as subprocesses,
not linked or redistributed) and bundles one small third-party helper script.

Bundled in this repository
--------------------------
* tools/jbig2topdf.py — from jbig2enc by Adam Langley, Apache License 2.0.
  Full license text: tools/jbig2enc-LICENSE.txt
  Source: https://github.com/agl/jbig2enc

Required external tools (install separately; NOT distributed here)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
* Ghostscript          — AGPL-3.0 (or commercial). https://www.ghostscript.com
* jbig2enc (`jbig2`)   — Apache-2.0.  https://github.com/agl/jbig2enc
* Tesseract OCR        — Apache-2.0.  https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract

Python dependencies (installed via pip; each under its own license)
-------------------------------------------------------------------
* ocrmypdf (MPL-2.0), pypdf (BSD), img2pdf (LGPL-3.0), Pillow (HPND/MIT-CMU),
  numpy (BSD), scipy (BSD).

Ghostscript is used only by executing the `gs` command; this project does not
link against or redistribute Ghostscript, so its AGPL terms are not imposed on
this MIT-licensed code. Users who redistribute Ghostscript binaries must comply
with the Ghostscript license themselves.
